      <title>土耳其埃尔多安升级反以色列言论，威胁干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/turkey-s-erdogan-escalates-anti-israel-rhetoric-with-threat-of-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安正在升级其对以色列的言论，暗示土耳其可能会代表巴勒斯坦进行干预，可能还会提供军事支持，其方式类似于土耳其在其他冲突中所做的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/turkey-s-erdogan-escalates-anti-israel-rhetoric-with-threat-of-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 20:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚加息争论将随通胀数据升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-rate-hike-debate-set-to-crescendo-with-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关于澳大利亚央行是否需要实施周期末期紧缩政策的争论很可能会在本周公布的季度通胀数据后得到解决 —— 而澳元也将受到波及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-rate-hike-debate-set-to-crescendo-with-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
